# Sales Analytics Dashboard

## Project Overview
This project analyzes sales data using SQL and Power BI.

## Tools Used
- SQL
- Power BI
- Excel (Data Cleaning)

## Files Included
- Sales Query.sql
- Sales Dashboard.pbix
- Sales Dashboard.pdf

## Key Insights
- Total Revenue: $1.6M
- Total Orders: 4000
- Highest Revenue Category: Home
- Most Popular Products: USB Cable, Yoga Mat, Perfume
- Revenue declined over months

## Skills Demonstrated
- SQL Query Writing
- Data Cleaning
- KPI Analysis
- Dashboard Design
- Business Insights

